research_municipality_step.notes: The Town of Anthony, TX operates under a Mayor/Aldermen system, which is a form of mayor-council government. Anthony Turner was identified as the current Mayor, elected in 2023. Louie Alfaro serves as the Mayor Pro Tem. Other elected council members include Stevens, Weeks, Flores, and Chavez. Full first names for council members Stevens, Weeks, Flores, and Chavez were not explicitly available in the search results. The specific council seat numbers for these individuals were also not consistently provided in the most recent sources.
